Class DescriptionBuilder.ListAppender

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.med.lom.foundation.util.DescriptionBuilder.Appender
      • gov.va.med.lom.foundation.util.DescriptionBuilder.ListAppender
  • Enclosing class:
    DescriptionBuilder

    protected static class DescriptionBuilder.ListAppender
extends DescriptionBuilder.Appender
    Describes the contents of a given List. Invokes DescriptionBuilder.append(java.lang.Object) on each of its elements. Add the separator (see DescriptionBuilder.Properties.getSeparator()) between all elements. The list is not sorted in anyway.
